title: 2019 NFL Draft Extravaganza
itunes:title: 2019 NFL Draft Extravaganza
description:
Dave Dameshek is joined by many 1st-Round Draft picks in Nashville, including Tampa Bay Buccaneers 5th overall pick Devin White (3:30), Pittsburgh Steelers 10th overall pick Devin Bush (11:30), New York Jets 3rd overall pick Quinnen Williams (18:15) & Detroit Lions 8th overall pick T.J. Hockenson (23:45). Plus, Eddie Spaghetti gives his thoughts on the Giants selection of Duke QB Daniel Jones with the 6th overall pick (30:10) and then the Duke signal caller joins the show to discuss being a member of the Giants (32:20). To close the show, Shek kibitzes with Miami Dolphins 13th overall pick Christian Wilkins (39:10).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
